"D:\Halo\Eldewrito\Game\maps\tags.dat"

CreateModPackage
Piggy Back
Allows you to piggy back on other players (You can even build a tower of power!)
Newbie
1.0
Multiplayer

## New string ids for our seat and seat camera markers
StringId Add piggyback
StringId Add piggyback_e
StringId Add piggyback_cam
StringId Add piggyback_cam_e
StringId Add mongoose_p_left_hand_e
StringId Add mongoose_p_left_foot_e
StringId Add mongoose_p_right_foot_e

## Animation mode for Chief piggyback (from mongoose_p)
EditTag objects\characters\masterchief\masterchief.model_animation_graph
CopyBlockElements Modes 51
PasteBlockElements Modes
SetField Modes[*].Name piggyback
SaveTagChanges
Exit

## Animation mode for elite piggyback (from mongoose_p)
EditTag objects\characters\dervish\dervish.model_animation_graph
CopyBlockElements Modes 78
PasteBlockElements Modes
SetField Modes[*].Name piggyback_e
SetField Modes[*].ModeIk[*].AttachToMarker mongoose_p_left_hand_e
AddBlockElements Modes[*].ModeIk
SetField Modes[*].ModeIk[*].Marker left_foot
SetField Modes[*].ModeIk[*].AttachToMarker mongoose_p_left_foot_e
AddBlockElements Modes[*].ModeIk
SetField Modes[*].ModeIk[*].Marker right_foot
SetField Modes[*].ModeIk[*].AttachToMarker mongoose_p_right_foot_e
SaveTagChanges
Exit

