PasteBlockElements MarkerGroups
SetField MarkerGroups[*].Name mongoose_p_left_foot
SetField MarkerGroups[*].Markers[0].Translation -0.1 0.1 0.1
CopyBlockElements MarkerGroups 1
PasteBlockElements MarkerGroups
SetField MarkerGroups[*].Name mongoose_p_left_foot_e
