## Chief add seat
EditTag objects\characters\masterchief\mp_masterchief\mp_masterchief.biped
AddBlockElements Seats
SetField Seats[*].Flags Driver,AllowsWeapons
SetField Seats[*].Label piggyback
SetField Seats[*].MarkerName piggyback
SetField Seats[*].EntryMarkerName body
SetField Seats[*].PingScale 1
SetField Seats[*].FlippedEvictionTime 32000
SetField Seats[*].AiSeatType Driver
SetField Seats[*].BoardingSeat -1
SetField Seats[*].UnitCamera.CameraMarkerName piggyback_cam
SetField Seats[*].EntryRadius 0.4
SetField Seats[*].EntryMarkerConeAngle 180
SetField Seats[*].EntryMarkerFacingAngle 45
SetField Seats[*].MaximumRelativeVelocity 1
SetField Seats[*].RuntimeInvisibleSeatRegionIndex -1
CopyBlockElements Seats 0
PasteBlockElements Seats
SetField Seats[*].Label piggyback_e
SetField Seats[*].MarkerName piggyback_e
SetField Seats[*].UnitCamera.CameraMarkerName piggyback_cam_e
SaveTagChanges
Exit

